{"tid":1679814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我正式宣佈 進入勝利大直路","createTime":"2019-10-28T11:54:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T15:25:03.000Z","uid":335712,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6ca7e86fbbbeed26cfa004f41aff3d68f3fe286f","tid":1679814,"uid":335712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:54:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">天時</span></strong></span><br />\n秋風起 天氣涼了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大量技能正式解鎖!!<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>水魔法</strong></span><br />\n千祈唔好喺寒冬之下同狗狗玩水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n會凍親啲狗狗架<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/fozen_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>隱身魔法</strong><br />\n<br />\n冬天最岩就係扮靚靚<br />\n著衫營造層次感 是但除一兩件就變到身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n再唔係一件風褸包晒全身<br />\n<br />\n天氣凍用頸巾圍下塊面 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個人當堂暖晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n出黎唔洗揹大背囊 著件大褸就得 有咩事就咁係個袋到拎出黎掉野走<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/36.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">火魔法</span><br />\n<br />\n風高物燥，提防祝融<br />\n<br />\n天氣乾起上黎樹葉柴枝都燒得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">風魔法</span><br />\n<br />\n天公造美 手足只需佔順風位 TG不攻自破<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><strong>心靈魔法</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n一年最有氣氛嘅兩個節日 聖誕新年<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">你班撚樣只能夠圍爐過 街都唔敢出親戚都唔敢見<br />\n做冬?做你老母!等我地同你開年啦死黑警</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>地利</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n一直都係喺我地呢邊<br />\n只係要小心啲CAM<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>人和</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n時至今日 全世界嘅先進國家幾乎都企係我地呢邊<br />\n港共 黑警 已經淪為世界過街老鼠<br />\n清算已成定局<br />\n<br />\n黃色經濟圈發揮作用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多次演練 和勇一體 無法被分化 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n支爆將至 已成現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">輸?帶定番梘等我幫你地沖身啦mon po狗</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f27c438ede5d202cfd042837f10efa3668f67f6d","tid":1679814,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:54:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7kDwBC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7kDwBC.jpg&h=6da1c92c&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"945c94ec02411a82fe423ef5928ab5993b844229","tid":1679814,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:56:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a889fbebc258ed0ce562f568fb857643089b4e2c","tid":1679814,"uid":200550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T11:56:29.000Z","msg":"話說西九龍聽日有手足上庭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1679742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1679742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b6c0825c733599edd54fa2ac25343fdc6f95ae5c","tid":1679814,"uid":335712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:06:38.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2484ee33ff049418b066ba914aacc963209e5b","tid":1679814,"uid":335712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-28T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/13.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}